text: Bjarne Jørgensen (born 13 May 1933) is a Danish gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1933 births Category:Living people Category:Danish male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Denmark Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Copenhagen
